title: Episode #1.1
description: On the day of her wedding, Meg Cummings finds out that her husband to be is having an affair with her best friend. She runs away from her wedding and Kansas. Now she wants to find the man she has been e-mailing.

title: Episode #1.83
description: There's a break-in at The Deep. Tim tells Annie he wants to talk about her suggestion of teaming up. Mr. Chang tells Casey that he wants to make him an heir.

title: Episode #1.84
description: A wounded Cole makes his way into a grotto and tells Caitlin what happened. Rae tells her parents that she and Casey aren't married so her father gives her an ultimatum. Ben tells Annie to move.

title: Episode #1.85
description: Olivia persuades Gregory to be Elaine's lawyer. Michael gets Virginia a job.

title: Episode #1.86
description: Time for court. Wei-Lee connives a disastrous dinner.

title: Episode #1.87
description: Gregory comes up with the idea of finding out who Elaine's son is whom the late Del kidnapped. Olivia accidentally reveals to Caitlin that she knows about her and Cole's plans to leave Sunset Beach.

title: Episode #1.88
description: Ricardo and Gabi try and persuade Paula not to move out. Caitlin try persuading her mom to give Cole the Deschanel jewels. Wei-Lee has a meeting with Gregory at the Grenadines.

title: Episode #1.89
description: Vanessa receives a proposition from Gregory to go to Hong Kong. Later, she gets jealous when she sees Michael and Virginia hug. Paula and Ricardo make up but Gabi is causing uneasiness in the house. Elaine and Cole have an important talk.

title: Episode #1.90
description: Casey finds out about Wei-Lee's business connection with Gregory. Joan (Meg's mother) comes to visit, all arranged and taken care of by Tim who - together with Annie - are planning to make Joan feel that her daughter has gotten into bad company.

title: Episode #1.96
description: Gabi accidentally reveals to someone about her fling with Ricardo. Paula finds out that half-brother Cole is wanted by Interpool. Jimmy shocks Michael when he tells him to stop coming on to his mother.

title: Episode #1.98
description: Cole and Caitlin finds a motel to live in. Gregory still has spies out there looking for them. Meg tries to get out of the room without anyone knowing that she's been in there and what she's seen.

title: Episode #1.99
description: Cole - accompanied by Caitlin - goes to see a person whom he hopes can answer his questions. Sean gets blurry vision again. Gregory badmouths Cole to Elaine but she refuses to believe what he says. Ricardo tries telling Paula about his fling with Gabi.

title: Episode #1.100
description: Just as Cole decides to go back to Sunset Beach for Elaine's trial, Julianna proclaims that she will go in his place instead because all this mess is her fault, she says. Gabi tells Paula about Ricardo cheating on her but doesn't reveal to her who with. It proves difficult for Meg to put the key back in the cigar box.

title: Episode #1.101
description: Julianna tells Cole to find out when it's time for court and she'll be there but Cole has made up his mind to go back to Sunset Beach despite his mother's offer. Paula sees Ricardo standing by the door and confronts him regarding what Gabi said. Rae thinks about what man to choose: Casey or Wei-Lee.
